### Q7: (5pt) For people who have got Bachelors degree, what the is percentage to have capital.gain more than 1000?

``` r
bachelorsdegree <- sum(adults$education == 'Bachelors')
capitalgain <- sum(adults$capital.gain > 1000)
(capitalgain/bachelorsdegree)*100
```

    ## [1] 49.61718
